![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1629921531479-JC5IFYVYFCMSAEBBRX4L/192.jpg?format=original)

With Shang-Chi quickly approaching Marvel is hoping to bust open the genre of Superhero martial arts! DC Comics has their fair share of incredibly skilled hand-to-hand combatants, and the very best of them are featured in the 40th DC Animated film Batman: Soul of The Dragon! The story follows Batman, Richard Dragon, Bronze Tiger, Lady Shiva, and others as they attempt to stop a world-ending threat. Join us as we follow this adventure set in the 1970s, full of kung fu, spy antics, and satanic cults in this fun and action-packed animated film!  
  
Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
